OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fpatchy cloud allowing plenty of bright
OL,7,Fand sunny spells. Winds will be light
OL,8,Fand feeling a little cooler than in
OL,9,Frecent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells becoming more prolonged as
OL,13,Fcloud clears. Remaining dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith mostly clear skies, leading to a
OL,15,Fcold night with a widespread frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,18,Fit will be a dry day with long spells
OL,19,Fof sunshine. Turning cloudier in the
OL,20,Fevening with some rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
